channel.title: Developer Needed!
channel.description:
Hi everyone,
I am looking for a developer for a new project. The developer does not have to be experienced, our server has great ideas planned. I do not care about the income; you will receive a larger percentile of the profit that is made.
PM me your skype if you're interested in taking part of this project.
Kind regards,
